OL,3,CCompany fined after two workers lose
OL,4,Cfingers in machinery
OL,6,FA bedding company has been fined more
OL,7,Fthan a quarter of a million pounds
OL,8,Fafter two employees suffered serious
OL,9,Finjuries when they were caught in
OL,10,Fmachinery.
OL,12,FSartex Quilts and Textiles Limited in
OL,13,FCastle Mill, Rochdale, was prosecuted
OL,14,Fby the (HSE) following the "serious
OL,15,Fand avoidable" incidents.
OL,17,FA 32-year-old man, from , lost three
OL,18,Ffingers on his first day working on
OL,19,Fthe line when he was cleaning the
OL,20,Fmeasuring wheel on a cutting machine.
