OL,6,FIn a victim personal statement he
OL,7,Fsaid: "Prior to this incident, I was a
OL,8,Fhealthy, happy and active person. At
OL,9,Fthe time I had one very young son, now
OL,10,FI have two children.
OL,12,F"I try not to expose my left hand too
OL,13,Fmuch to my children when I am playing
OL,14,Fwith them or when they are in my
OL,15,Fcompany.
OL,17,F"I do not talk about the incident with
OL,18,Fmy children. When I am out and about
OL,19,Fin public, I try to keep my injured
OL,20,Fhand out of the public view."
