OL,6,FA 51-year-old from lost the tips of
OL,7,Ftwo of his fingers after his glove
OL,8,Fbecame tangled in a machine, causing
OL,9,Fhis right hand to be dragged in.
OL,11,FThe incidents were investigated by the
OL,12,FHSE who found the company did not
OL,13,Fguard the machinery and did not
OL,14,Fimplement suitable and sufficient
OL,15,Fprocedures to isolate machinery from
OL,16,Fpower.
OL,18,FThe company was fined #251,250 and
OL,19,Fordered to pay #6,862.63 in costs at
OL,20,FManchester & Salford Magistrates'
OL,21,FCourt on 14 February 2024.
