OL,6,FAfter the hearing, HSE inspector Elena
OL,7,FPickford said: "These injuries were
OL,8,Fserious and avoidable, the risk should
OL,9,Fhave been identified.
OL,11,F"Employers should make sure they
OL,12,Fproperly assess and ensure that access
OL,13,Fto dangerous parts of machinery are
OL,14,Fprevented.
OL,16,F"Had these machines been adequately
OL,17,Fguarded and a safe isolating procedure
OL,18,Fbeen in place, these incidents could
OL,19,Fhave easily been prevented."
